  "text": "Nonetheless, AF is a chronically progressive disease. In the ESC guidelines, the five clinical subtypes of AF encompass the progression from undiagnosed episodes through first diagnosis and infrequent paroxysms to long-lasting persistent and eventually permanent AF [CITATION_1] (Box 1).",
